d in significant \'life moments\' of those around - births (at home), birthdays, death</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Into the nineties</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>About this time the streetscape starts to change from a quiet country back lane to high density. More traffic - speed. Hedges and old world gardens (even a habitat tree) come down. Some barriers go up.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>More private ownership - dual occupancy - childless professional couples - high turnover of student houses - busy lifestyles - little time or interest in \'the street\' - more locking up - more franchised services - less sharing and involvement in the street - a community in the balance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Liz, Way Street, 1986-1997 (contributed 1996)</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'A community in the balance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '208-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-04 08:06:53', '2021-10-04 08:06:53', '', 208, 'http://localhost:8888/WP/example/Wordpress/?p=209', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
