 Street and which is now the stormwater drain.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class="wp-block-buttons"><!-- wp:button {"fontSize":"small"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-button has-custom-font-size has-small-font-size"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="http://localhost:8888/WP/example/Wordpress/suicide-hill/">View</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:heading {"fontSize":"normal"} -->\n<h2 class="has-normal-font-size">Visiting</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The first encounter that I had, personally, with the Tocumwal houses, was in 1948, when they were very new. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class="wp-block-buttons"><!-- wp:button {"fontSize":"small"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-button has-custom-font-size has-small-font-size"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="http://localhost:8888/WP/example/Wordpress/visiting/">View</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:heading {"fontSize":"normal"} -->\n<h2 class="has-normal-font-size">Todd Street ceilidhs</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When Barty’s children were 21 we had a party and when my children were 21 we had a party and just for the hell of it we had a party.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class="wp-block-buttons"><!-- wp:button {"fontSize":"small"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-button has-custom-font-size has-small-font-size"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="http://localhost:8888/WP/example/Wordpress/todd-street-ceilidhs/">View</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:heading {"fontSize":"normal"} -->\n<h2 class="has-normal-font-size">Square dancing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When we went square dancing sometimes they’d come back here and it’d be nothing to have 40 or 50 people in the lounge room here.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class="wp-block-buttons"><!-- wp:button {"fontSize":"small"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-button has-custom-font-size has-small-font-size"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="http://localhost:8888/WP/example/Wordpress/square-dancing/">View</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:heading {"fontSize":"normal"} -->\n<h2 class="has-normal-font-size">Dances and a keg of beer</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We used to have a party occasionally. Alice was very good on the accordion.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class="wp-block-buttons"><!-- wp:button {"fontSize":"small"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-button has-custom-font-size has-small-font-size"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="http://localhost:8888/WP/example/Wordpress/dances-and-a-keg-of-beer/">View</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:heading {"fontSize":"normal"} -->\n<h2 class="has-normal-font-size">Sunday at the Raccosta’s</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the early days, because there were so few of us, every Sunday afternoon, the Italian families would get together in our big room and have a dance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class="wp-block-buttons"><!-- wp:button {"fontSize":"small"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-button has-custom-font-size has