 -->\n<div class="wp-block-buttons"><!-- wp:button {"fontSize":"small"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-button has-custom-font-size has-small-font-size"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="http://localhost:8888/WP/example/Wordpress/this-housell-suit-me-fine/">View</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:heading {"fontSize":"normal"} -->\n<h2 class="has-normal-font-size">A community in the balance</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When we moved in there was more government housing with larger families. At one stage about 11 children who played together in ever-growing groups</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class="wp-block-buttons"><!-- wp:button {"fontSize":"small"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-button has-custom-font-size has-small-font-size"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="http://localhost:8888/WP/example/Wordpress/a-community-in-the-balance/">View</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Changing patterns of community from the 1970s-1990s', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '204-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-04 13:57:54', '2021-10-04 13:57:54', '', 204, 'http://localhost:8888/WP/example/Wordpress/?p=237', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
